<assessmentItem xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqti_v2p1" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqti_v2p1 imsqti_v2p1.xsd" identifier="advice_when_lifecit_difficult" title="Advice" adaptive="false" timeDependent="false">
  <stylesheet type="text/css" href="lifecit_logo.css"/><stylesheet href="advice_when_lifecit_difficult.css" type="text/css"/>
  <itemBody><include xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="lifecit_logo.lgtp" parse="xml"/>
    <div id="container-body">&#160;<div><img id="image-1" alt="change me" src="grey_box.jpg"/></div><div id="textbox-19" class="includeBorderAndPadding"><span class="textbox-19-style1">It seems that you haven't reached all of your goals today</span><br/></div><div id="textbox-20" class="includeBorderAndPadding"><ul> <li><span class="textbox-20-style1"><span class="textbox-20-style2">Talk to someone </span>- letting someone know you are finding it hard may help with finding ways to making it better.</span></li></ul> <ul> <li><span class="textbox-20-style3">Try <span class="textbox-20-style4">easier activities and exercises</span>, or do <span class="textbox-20-style5">less</span>. It may be that you are aiming too high.</span></li></ul> <ul> <li><span class="textbox-20-style6">Take <span class="textbox-20-style7">breaks</span> and do something you enjoy.<br/></span></li></ul> <ul> <li><span class="textbox-20-style8">Make sure you <span class="textbox-20-style9">reward yourself </span>- it can be hard work!</span></li></ul> <ul> <li><span class="textbox-20-style10"><span class="textbox-20-style11">Give out your username</span> to your therapist, friends and relatives. They will then be able to send you messages of encouragement.<br/></span></li></ul><span class="textbox-20-style12"><br/></span></div><div><img id="image-2" alt="Support" src="-bad-news.jpg"/></div><div id="button-1" class="submit-button">Next</div><div id="textbox-21" class="includeBorderAndPadding"><div class="textbox-21-style1"><span class="textbox-21-style2">What can I do if I am finding it hard?</span><span class="textbox-21-style3"> - Some Tips</span><br/></div></div><div id="button-2" class="submit-button">Back</div></div>
  </itemBody>
</assessmentItem>